pineapples</link> in <symbol wordnetid="106806469" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../270/13270.xml">
Hawaii</link></symbol>
, no <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../393/38393.xml">
rubber</link> trees in Africa, no <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../307/5307.xml">
cattle</link> in <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
